Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛我非要去那个破烂教会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教那些小鬼读书认字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介才更适合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不干
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 和我换如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也被安排了工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要好好清理破烂教会阁楼上的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 今天只能陪着小鬼们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们这群小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给我坐下 老老实实听我讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上过学吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没上过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连学都没上过的人 还想给我们上课？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为我们是烟花巷里的小孩 就把我们当笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂你们几个 给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:06.34,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}本片字幕由异域字幕组(www.yydm.com)制作,仅供试看之用,如果喜欢本作品,请购买并支持正版!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:11.01,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻译： 生姜 定口 天井 雨意  校译 : 影子  时间/后期 : V  压制: 茶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃老师 给我读读这本书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&H2AB6DF&\3c&H855C50&\pos(672.001,509.334)}青    鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:30.86,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,溢れ出す激情　打ち当たるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:30.86,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,溢出的激情 若要被它击中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:41.37,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,はじけろ　宙に刻む願いよ wonder fang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:41.37,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,迸发吧 铭刻于空中的愿望 预想以上的毒牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:53.09,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,油断させては牙を剥く　何らかの代償を着て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:53.09,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,让你放松警惕才露出毒牙 披着某种代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:58.12,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,不穏な笑みを滲ませ　覚醒させる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:58.12,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,流露出危险的微笑 让你觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:03.90,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,どの縄張りに過去を落とし　いつ掬い出せるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:03.90,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不知把过去丢在心中的那一块 不知何时又会被捞出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:09.94,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,同じ記憶から手繰り寄せ　必ずその手掴むんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:09.94,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,从相同的记忆开始吸引过来 一定要把那双手抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:18.12,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,キミの中の僕　僕の中のキミは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:18.12,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,你里面的我 我里面的你是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:20.06,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,誰だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:20.06,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:25.45,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,鋭才のウィザード　匂う魂の鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:25.45,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,锐才的魔法使 勾魂之鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:31.00,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,叫び続けるよ　まだ諦めないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:31.00,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我会叫喊下去 还不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:36.31,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,激り込んだ熱情　切り裂いたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:36.31,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,激流涌入般的热情 若是把它撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:48.07,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,舞い散れ　宙に鳴いた祈りは wonder bond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:48.07,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,飞舞零落 在空中回响的祈愿是 预想以上的毒牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是佳穗酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一出生就失明了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近她貌似对外国童话很着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以找一些给她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青鸟…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是旧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面还有缺页呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是小时候看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概的故事还是能讲给她听的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过佳穗应该是个认生的小孩才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然能主动和你亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 我已经答应她明天给她念了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是没办法的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你对其他的小孩也那么亲切就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 他们没上过学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨 这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶们还是一如既往那么吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连户籍都没有 出生在烟花巷的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会那么轻易地去上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是蠢得可以了 白天还让那些孩子都跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是在帮倒忙 小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳穗酱一定会很期待明天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺页的地方 你一定要好好记起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚要住在教会 你就先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会帮你清理老鼠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 今晚只能去古那屋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这不是教会的小子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来个包子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天我没带钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 专门付钱的小哥没在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家出的新品 帮着尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧吃吧 给我说说感想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱味？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应真是冷淡啊 这个不好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒不是  我更喜欢再重口些的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介会加乳酪 还会把煮鸡蛋也放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乳酪还有煮鸡蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做新口味的话 还不如做红烧肉包和泡菜肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节的话 栗子南瓜包也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 我们出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圣诞夜 吉尔和梅迪兄妹一起去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去寻找传说中幸福的青鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途中 两个人在回忆之国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到了已经去世的爷爷奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有年幼的弟弟妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么长时间都不来看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想来而不能来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只要还能记起我们就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我们不管什么时候 睁开眼睛就能见到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要换一本书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能回忆起长相和名字都不知道的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要回忆就能见到最重要的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄 今天回来的好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 吵醒你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你今晚也去古那屋那里过夜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 还是不适合教小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又被他们逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你和佳穗酱越来越亲密了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳穗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她问我怎么才能回忆起连长相和名字都不知道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她刚出生的时候就被丢在店门前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳穗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:08:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 身在花街还要养育孩子 一定很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的事情自己都能处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却无法回忆连长相和名字都不知道的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就算是去了回忆之国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道哪个是自己的父母 也见不到他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲的事 你一点都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去大塚村之前的事 我一点也不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 连妈妈的脸都有点记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还隐约记得一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的脸和你很像 气质也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是去了回忆之国 我绝对能找到你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能去 在回忆之国里也没有我想见的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天重新做了样品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你帮忙尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是加了乳酪的咖喱包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还放了一个水煮鹌鹑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 这个能大卖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就根据我的形象 起名叫华丽男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡菜的也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我更喜欢有虾米和韭菜的泡菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栗子南瓜包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个稍微甜了些 乳酪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一口气都说了我记不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写在这上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来不怕你笑话 大叔我基本不会读写
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能顺便帮大叔记下配方就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我写了 你不会读也白费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让老婆孩子读给我听啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 真的是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然一本正经起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 多亏了小哥 我才想出了新产品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好保存在家里的佛龛里供奉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒 我们回房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳穗要怎样才能学会读书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想读的书 我可以读给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思 佳穗在想佳穗为什么要叫佳穗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳穗是谁给你取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字和佳穗一起被扔在店门口了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是父母给取的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳穗的佳 有美人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗是稻穗的穗 经常用来给女孩子命名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含着对丰收的向往和祝愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是佳穗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 佳穗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 刚辉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚辉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚是钻石的意思 真是霸气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也看不见有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正怎么跟你说都是对牛弹琴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费口舌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 佳穗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一个大男孩居然先哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你一个女孩子如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说大叔说的新产品什么时候上市啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新产品？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？难道还在保密吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前还很认真地在记秘密配方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是装饰在佛龛上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 记笔记的人是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 快去看佛龛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家现在就想吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拜托我做的便当 中午送过去可以不？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说最近都没看到信乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最近在教会给孩子们上课
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小目 你也很孤单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大概都没吃上几顿好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大黑堂的老板每天都会送慰问品到教会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以信乃很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大黑堂？为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是信乃和老板有缘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？大黑堂的老板不是一个月前就去世了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃和老板是什么时候认识的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听信乃说 好像是一周前还每天都见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近大黑堂因为新食品很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天门前都大排长龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我知道 华丽男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸去世时 还以为这家店赚不了钱要关门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\c&H1A1C1C&\3c&HD7DEDD&\pos(733.334,344)}已卖完             抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他留下了秘方 所以我们也不能放弃这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么华丽男 超级男的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H010101&\3c&H314A41&\fs70\pos(848,365.333)}大\N黑\N堂\N遗\N书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000300&\3c&H3B524A&\fs55\pos(365.333,621.333)}大\N黑\N喜\N平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是怎么和那个孩子决定名称的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介老师 信乃老师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他过会儿就来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介 芋头已经给孩子们分完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了 毛野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 孩子们老是在争哪个芋头大哪个芋头小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对他们总是这么有耐心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天他们很乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个这么漂亮姐姐来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能大家都有点紧张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我不是漂亮姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一块芋头好像烤好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 庄介老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子完全看不见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因此她的感觉也更加敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时候不太能应付她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你这伪善的笑脸 居然对小孩子很有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为佳穗看不见 我再怎么摆笑脸也无济于事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像今天毛野 不是也无视了佳穗么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对于大人的这种情感 孩子们也很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那个孩子更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是生你的气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那个孩子从一开始就对信乃很热情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得真是不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 庄介 你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不烫吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从五年前的那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多第二天也就痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为只是因为自己对于疼痛比较不敏感而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来好像并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介老师 在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳穗 我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来找我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又温柔又宽厚的手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手掌却是冰冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的午饭是古那屋老板特意准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 居然是古那屋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为古那屋的老板和信乃老师关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以特地请他为大家做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给这些小鬼吃简直是暴殄天物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笃志和佳穗 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们二人是本月的寿星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿信乃老师还会为大家献歌一曲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有听人说话啊 庄介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大部分都记下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳穗 你想读哪本书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是「青鸟」啊 之前不是刚读过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:19:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为信乃老师每次讲的都不太一样 很有意思呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终 没能找到「青鸟」的两人踏上归途回到家中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才终于了解至今为止的平淡生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他们来说才是无上的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄…庄介老师让我给你们送蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字 笃志的汉字要怎么写
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笃志 也读作tokushi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tokushi？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是指拥有温柔善良和内心坚强的人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全比不上这名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙可不是那种美好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了 佳穗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃老师 青色是什么样的颜色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青色啊 是天空的颜色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青色是温柔的颜色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哟 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 难道说你的眼睛看不见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和庄介老师一样的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是庄介的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳穗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个有深蕴的名字啊 是谁给你取的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是信乃老师告诉我「kaho」就是佳穗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃？果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好珍惜这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它将成为你强力的守护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 我也是「庄介」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 现在就叫我「苍」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了 佳穗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和庄介老师一样温柔的手掌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 却很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:06.02,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}一人にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:06.02,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}不要让我孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:09.52,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甘く　甘く色をとって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:09.52,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甜美地 绽放色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:13.19,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:13.19,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要轻易离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:17.57,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕の命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:17.57,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你就是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:24.45,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どうしてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:24.45,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:29.75,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}どうして君の願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:29.75,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}到底是为什么 你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:35.09,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみの雨に打たれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:35.09,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}虽被悲伤之雨淋透
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:36.84,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}咲いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:36.84,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}却依旧傲然怒放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:43.97,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう大事なもの傷つけたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:43.97,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}已经不能伤害重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:48.48,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その静かな笑顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:48.48,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只想默默守候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:52.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:52.23,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你那恬静的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:56.07,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:56.07,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}伸出你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:22:59.61,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独さえ壊すほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:22:59.61,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}去打破孤寂的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:02.74,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終焉の時も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:02.74,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}直到终结之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:05.62,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君がいるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:05.62,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只要有你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:07.33,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怖くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:07.33,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我就不会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:10.71,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:10.71,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只有你能照亮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:15.80,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}ただ一つの光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:15.80,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}是我唯一的光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说信乃你在教会当老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是教小孩子无聊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教大人就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请教导身为大人的我各种事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃的那样的事这样的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.57,0:23:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡警先生 有变态啊！
